response.original_title: High Hopes: The Anatomy of a Winner
response.overview: Larry Andersen and John Kruk lead a behind-the-scenes journey of the 1993 National League Champion Philadelphia Phillies, from the first workout of Spring Training through the final pitch of the World Series. This video contains game highlights, as well as never-before-seen clubhouse footage, along with retrospective interviews with players, coaches, broadcasters, and opponents.
response.title: High Hopes: The Anatomy of a Winner
